{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a3f9218f95","title":"关于模特儿问题的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"00c0c4ea60","index":0,"year":1965,"month":7,"day":18,"articleId":"a3f9218f95"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"27fe8fe018","type":"title","text":"关于模特儿问题的批示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"a3f9218f95"},{"id":"c5a1fb585f","type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少裸体模特儿是绘画和雕塑必须的基本功，不要不行。封建思想加以禁止是不妥的。即使有些坏事出现，也不要紧，为了艺术科学，不惜少有牺牲。齐白石、陈半丁之流，就花木而论，还不如清末某些画家。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"a3f9218f95"},{"id":"aced6c7852","type":"paragraph","text":"中国画家，就我见过的，只有一个徐悲鸿留了人体素描，其余如齐白石、陈半丁之流，","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"a3f9218f95"},{"id":"1d0c28d2b3","type":"paragraph","text":"没有一个人能画人物的。徐悲鸿学过西洋画法，此外还有一个刘海粟。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"a3f9218f95"}],"page":{"id":"bc9a9d34ab","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"a3f9218f95","start":444,"end":444}}}},"__N_SSG":true}